        <article class="clearfix">
            <div class="single-post indienova-single-post fr-view">
                <h4><strong>快速介绍</strong></h4><p>不详细介绍的几款游戏：</p><ul><li><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/866800/The_Walking_Dead_The_Final_Season/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">《行尸走肉》的最后一季</a></li><li>绿光时期熬过来的平台跳跃独立游戏 <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/817710/vridniX/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">vridniX</a> （支持中文）</li><li>霓虹漂移赛车游戏 <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/897400/Driftpunk_Racer/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Driftpunk Racer</a></li><li>场景挺好看的 VR 休闲抓东西游戏 <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/895890/GrabBag/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">GrabBag</a></li><li>《黎明杀机》开发组新作 <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/555440/DEATHGARDEN/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">DEATHGARDEN™</a> （还是非对称竞技1v5）</li></ul><p>那么！正篇开始！</p><h4><strong>Evergarden 心灵花园</strong></h4><p>关键词：休闲、解谜</p><p>发售日期：8月17日</p><p>一款精致的益智游戏，解开各式各样的的谜题，和可爱守护者一起为花园注入生命吧！</p><p>本作支持中文。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/8/Evergarden1.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="8547" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/8/Evergarden2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="8548" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/8/Evergarden3.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="8549" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/576500/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4><strong>State of Mind 意志之国</strong></h4><p>关键词：赛博朋克、反乌托邦、冒险</p><p>发售日期：8月15日</p><p>“当思维和机器成为一体时——人类还剩下什么？”</p><p>本作和已发售的《红弦俱乐部》所讨论的有点相似。在 State of Mind 里，玩家扮演一名对世界状况不满的记者理查德·诺兰，当遭遇了一起爆炸后，他在医院里醒来，发现他的妻儿已经神秘地消失。已经无法再袖手旁观了。</p><p>本作支持中文。</p><p>站内相关文章：<a href="https://indienova.com/indie-game-news/state-of-mind/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">《STATE OF MIND：超人类主义下的二元分裂世界》</a></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/8/State of Mind1.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="8543" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/8/State of Mind2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="8544" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/8/State of Mind3.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="8545" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/437630/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4><strong>Not Tonight 今晚没开</strong></h4><p>关键词：模拟、政治、点击</p><p>发售日期：8月17日</p><blockquote><p>在个另类的英国，脱欧谈判失败了，一个极右翼的政府夺取权力。政府就开始了排欧裔政策，把欧裔人都兜捕而遣送出境。在这个情况之下，你失去了你的舒适生活，现在得在繁荣地短工经济内过活赚吃，找个方法回去你的老家。</p></blockquote><p>一款类似 Paper，Please 的游戏，这一次的情境是担任一名门卫。游戏自带中文，不过就 steam 页面的中文质量来看可能会有一些别扭。</p><p>同时笔者在搜寻资料的时候，发现该游戏<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=a8jtPQY3_fw" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">在 youtube 上的宣传片</a>评论区一片骂声，原因是该视频关闭了赞/踩数据显示。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/8/Not Tonight1.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="8539" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/8/Not Tonight2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="8540" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/8/Not Tonight3.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="8541" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/733790/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4><strong>Sword Legacy Omen</strong></h4><p>关键词：RPG、策略</p><p>发售日期：8月14日</p><p>不支持中文。游戏用有点血腥的方式讲述了另一个“亚瑟王传奇”。在落魄流浪中率领一群不太合得来的同伴，跨越困难寻找圣剑，拯救家园！</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/8/Sword Legacy Omen.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="8550" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/8/Sword Legacy Omen2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="8551" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/8/Sword Legacy Omen3.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="8552" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/690140/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4><strong>Graveyard Keeper 守墓人</strong></h4><p>关键词：经营、生存工艺</p><p>发售日期：8月15日</p><p>在星露谷里经营过自己的农场庄园后，这次来试试做一位守墓人吧！你是否要利用逝者来让自己赚的盆满钵满呢？甚至不惜为此杀人，以增加墓地的规模。表面上精致的像素游戏，背后隐含着道德抉择困境。</p><p>本站之前已经有一篇详细介绍：<a href="https://indienova.com/indie-game-news/graveyard-keeper-preview/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">《你一定没有经营过墓园》</a></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/8/Graveyard Keeper1.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="8595" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/8/Graveyard Keeper2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="8596" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/8/Graveyard Keeper3.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="8597" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/599140/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4><strong>Reventa</strong></h4><p>关键词：EA、动作</p><p>发售日期：8月15日</p><p>一场毁灭性的战争之后，人类的幸存者们逃亡到轨道站上的殖民地中，被留在地球上的拾荒者们在残骸中挣扎求生。你接收到一项回收技术的任务，并踏上旅程。</p><p>本作看起来十分酷炫，持刀女主角也为游戏增色不少。不过细看还是能发现游戏的品质仍有一些欠缺，希望在 EA 阶段完毕之后能给玩家一个惊喜。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/8/Reventa.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="8556" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/627890/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4><strong>Death's Gambit 死神诡计</strong></h4><p>关键词：魂 like、类银河战士恶魔城、RPG</p><p>发售日期：8月14日</p><p>不支持中文。本作可以被称为2D 像素版的黑魂了，在 E3、PAX 发售时便受到了很多关注。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/8/Death's Gambit1.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="8553" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/8/Death's Gambit2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="8554" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/8/Death's Gambit3.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="8555" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/356650/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4><strong>Phantom Doctrine 幽灵教义</strong></h4><p>关键词：回合制策略、潜行、RPG</p><p>发售日期：8月15日</p><p>本作支持中文。</p><p>故事发生在冷战时期，你将担任一家秘密组织的首脑，除了组织的名称是“密谋团”以外，外界对其几乎一无所知。通过完成秘密任务、调查机密文件和审讯敌方特工，一个邪恶的计划逐渐浮出水面。时间紧迫，必须阻止那些阴谋家，才能将世界从无法想象的命运边缘及时抢救回来。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/8/Phantom Doctrine1.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="8557" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/8/Phantom Doctrine2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="8558" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/8/Phantom Doctrine3.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="8559" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/559100/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4><strong>Destination Primus Vita - Episode 1: Austin</strong></h4><p>关键词：太空、解谜、叙事</p><p>发售日期：8月17日</p><p>本作支持中文，讲述了一个六人小团队在宇宙中穿梭，找回被外来生物带走的水源以拯救地球。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/8/Destination Primus Vita - Episode 1- Austin1.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="8563" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/8/Destination Primus Vita - Episode 1 Austin2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="8564" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/8/Destination Primus Vita - Episode 1 Austin3.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="8565" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/680750/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p>
            </div>
        </article>
    </div>

